        "created_at": "2016-06-21T16:25:30.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Any intel on this relatively new label from the folks at Dominus? A couple bottles of the '12 popped up at my local wine store and the owner has stated this is one of the best new labels to come out in recent years. I trust his knowledge and experience, but I wonder if this is due to the quality of the winemaker, or terroir, or perhaps they were fortunate to launch their first two vintages in 12 and 13? Perhaps all three?</p>",
