        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/i/f05b48/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-06-21T16:39:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Haven\u2019t had it yet, but hope to. It\u2019s an Oakville property, not far from ToKalon and Martha\u2019s Vineyard. Parker and Galloni rated it a 93, which is odd since both gave Dominus significantly higher scores. Buy one and try before buying. I know only 800 cases were made, but I don\u2019t see the 2012 flying off the shelf.</p>",
